episodes.title: LEAVING SCIENTOLOGY and Fighting the Gender Cult! MIKEroaggress’d Live with @Cbucksrules
episodes.description:
Jennifer grew up inside Scientology. She was hand-picked to serve as a personal bodyguard for Tom Cruise and David Miscavige, with one core job: ensure nobody ever leaves.

Now, years after breaking free from that cult, she’s sounding the alarm on what she sees as the next one rising: gender ideology.

I am so incredibly excited to delve deep into Jen’s story! You do not want to miss this one!
